nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values: A young nurse stands beside a blue demon in a hospital setting, her facial expression one of surprise with her eyes wide open. She has fair and smooth skin, and her hair is short and straight, although it was initially described as long blue hair. She wears a fitted, sleeveless black and red dress with distinctive red trim that accentuates her figure. The blue demon, with a ferocious expression, features long, pointed red horns and sharp teeth. It wears a loose, red and black robe and has one hand firmly grasping the nurse's waist, pulling her close to its side. The atmosphere of the image is dark and mysterious, with the nurse and demon positioned prominently against the backdrop of a hospital.

nodes.title: README
widgets_values:
Amazing Z-Image Workflow v2.1

## Workflow Prerequisites ##

 This workflow requires the following custom nodes, which can be obtained via ComfyUI-Manager:

  * rgthree      : https://github.com/rgthree/rgthree-comfy
  * ComfyUI-GGUF : https://github.com/city96/ComfyUI-GGUF

 Additionally, ensure you have the following three models downloaded and placed in their respective
 directories within your ComfyUI installation:

  z_image_turbo-Q5_K_S.gguf
    * Download: https://huggingface.co/jayn7/Z-Image-Turbo-GGUF/blob/main/z_image_turbo-Q5_K_S.gguf
    * Local Directory: `ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models/`

  Qwen3-4B.i1-Q5_K_S.gguf
    * Download: https://huggingface.co/mradermacher/Qwen3-4B-i1-GGUF/blob/main/Qwen3-4B.i1-Q5_K_S.gguf
    * Local Directory: `ComfyUI/models/text_encoders/`

  ae.safetensors
    * Download: https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/blob/main/split_files/vae/ae.safetensors
    * Local Directory: `Comfyui/models/vae/`

## More Info ##
   - https://github.com/martin-rizzo/AmazingZImageWorkflow
   - https://civitai.com/models/2181458/amazing-z-image-workflow


Created by Martin Rizzo  
  GitHub : https://github.com/martin-rizzo
  CivitAI: https://civitai.com/user/Photographer
  Reddit : https://www.reddit.com/user/FotografoVirtual
